    Output Format:
    Return a JSON object with the following structure:
    {
      "routeName": "string",
      "totalDistance": "string",
      "totalDuration": "string",
      "summary": "string explaining the route logic",
      "stops": [
        {
          "day": number,
          "city": "string",
          "activity": "short description of recommended action",
          "profitabilityJustification": "detailed explanation of why this stop is profitable based on search data",
          "demandScore": number (0-100),
          "trendVelocity": "string (e.g. 🔥 Exploding)",
